# Client Financial Performance Analysis

## Objective
Financial analysis of six months of client-wise profitability data.

## Dataset
The dataset covers financial records of 30 clients over a six-month period (January to June), including revenue, operational expenses, administrative expenses, gross profit, and net profit.

## Columns
- Revenue  
- Operational Cost  
- Gross Profit  
- Administrative Expense  
- Net Profit  

## Tasks Performed
The following analyses were conducted on the client-wise financial data:

- Calculation of gross profit margin ratio  
- Calculation of net profit margin ratio  
- Analysis of operational and administrative expenses  
- Client-wise monthly revenue analysis  
- Month-wise average net profit ratio  
- Visualization of monthly revenue and net profit trends  

## Tools Used
- Python  
- Pandas  
- Jupyter Notebook  

## Key Learnings
This project helped develop practical skills in:

- Data handling and manipulation  
- Importing and exporting datasets  
- Creating and modifying financial columns  
- Performing financial calculations and deriving insights  
- Applying Python to real-world style data analysis  

